title: 07/16/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 07/16/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP is joined by the MMQB's Albert Breer. With NFL Training camp quickly approaching, what's the latest on Deshaun Watson? The Golf Channel's Brandel Chamblee checks in to discuss Bryson DeChambeau's frustration with his driver. And with Kevin Love and Bradley Beal now out of the Olympics, Chris Haynes calls in to discuss possible replacements.
